        <item>
            <title>Zeekr 009 Deluxe 兩驅版抵港，內櫳豪華舒適 + 空氣懸掛可升降 45mm</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/14/zeekr009-deluxe-hk-launch/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=zeekr009-deluxe-hk-launch</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/14/zeekr009-deluxe-hk-launch/life-tech/auto/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[arthur]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 14 Mar 2025 14:15:23 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[汽車科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[MPV]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Zeekr]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Zeekr 009]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[極氪]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1297546</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>由錦龍汽車集團代理的高端電動車品牌 Zeekr 在香港正式推出全新 Zeekr 009 Deluxe 雙電版本，進一步豐富其在港市場的產品陣容。這款豪華電動 MPV 以「Every Seat Matters」為設計理念，專為家庭及商務用家打造頂級舒適與尖端科技體驗。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1297586" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250313_155556-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250313_155556-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250313_155556-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Zeekr 009 Deluxe &#8211; Launch Edition 搭載高效雙電機系統，提供最大馬力 335 hp（250 kW） 及 373 Nm 峯值扭力，從 0-100 km/h 加速僅需 7.9 秒，展現出色動力表現。配備 116 kWh 大容量電池，續航里程達 604 公里（WLTP） 或 740 公里（CLTC），足以應付長途出行需求。此外，支援 150 kW 直流快充，可在短時間內迅速補充電量，兼顧效率與便利。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1297585" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250313_155534-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250313_155534-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250313_155534-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1297587" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250313_155601-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250313_155601-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250313_155601-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Zeekr 009 Deluxe 雙電版的內飾設計奢華，車廂採用高級物料打造，配備六座獨立座椅，每位乘客都能享受寬敞舒適的乘坐體驗。第二排座椅更提供電動調節、通風、加熱及按摩功能，媲美頭等艙享受。車內搭載 15.4 吋中控觸控屏幕，及全液晶儀錶板，支援智能語音控制及 OTA 在線升級，讓駕駛者輕鬆掌控車輛狀態。此外， 009 Deluxe 採用單腔空氣懸掛，可升高降低 45mm，實現市場上其中一款最低平台（離地 37.2mm）的豪華 MPV，方便乘客輕鬆進出車輛。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1297588" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250313_160741-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250313_160741-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250313_160741-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1297590" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250313_160751-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250313_160751-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250313_160751-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1297589" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250313_160744-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250313_160744-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250313_160744-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>科技配置方面，Zeekr 009 配備 L2+ 級智能駕駛輔助系統，包括自適應巡航控制、車道保持輔助及自動泊車功能，大幅提升行車安全與便利性。此外，車輛內置 30 個 YAMAHA 環迴立體聲高級音響系統、17 吋吸頂屏幕及全景天幕，為乘客帶來影音娛樂與開揚空間感。行李空間靈活多變，後排座椅放平後可提供充足儲物容量，滿足家庭出遊或商務運輸的多樣需求。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1297567" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/009spev-694x333.png" alt="" width="694" height="333" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/009spev-694x333.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/009spev.png 1050w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>新車定價由 HK$650,000 起，即日起接受預訂。想了解 Zeekr 009 更多資料，可到 Zeekr 太古城展示廳（每日 09:00-19:30）或 Zeekr Space 理光中心（每日 09:00-19:00）參觀，另有位於新界荃灣的 Zeekr 品牌體驗中心（星期一至六 09:00-18:30）提供試駕服務。</p><p>查詢熱線：2111 1009。</p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/03/14/zeekr009-deluxe-hk-launch/life-tech/auto/">Zeekr 009 Deluxe 兩驅版抵港，內櫳豪華舒適 + 空氣懸掛可升降 45mm</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
