            <title>【評測】Samsung 全新中階機 Galaxy A56 / A36 極速抵港，新色搶眼 + 更多 AI 功能下放 + 開售詳情公佈</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/14/samsung-launch-galaxy-a56-a36-hong-kong/review-2/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=samsung-launch-galaxy-a56-a36-hong-kong</link>
