            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1297652</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>就在上星期，筆者才在西班牙巴塞舉行的 MWC 大會中，為大家報導過 Samsung 低調現身的兩部全新 A 系中階手機 Galaxy A56 及 Galaxy A36，沒想到 Samsung 今日已正式在香港發佈，而且亦公佈了開售詳情，現在就讓 Edward 帶大家到現場睇睇啦。</p><h2>雙 A 顏色搶眼仍針對年青族羣</h2><p>對 Samsung 手機有一定認知的讀者，應該都會知道 A 系是屬於中階機款，而且一向主打年青用家族羣，去到今代的 Galaxy A56 及 A36 亦不例外。今次兩部 A 系新機，機背均採用了強化玻璃配以鮮艷顏色作設計，當中較入門的 Galaxy A36 設有兩個規格：8 + 128GB 版本設有亮夜黑及亮薰紫兩隻顏色，而 8 + 256GB 版本就除了這兩隻顏色外，更設有亮冰白及亮青綠兩隻顏色。至於較高階的 Galaxy A56 就只設 12 + 256GB 一個規格，設有霧炭灰、霧墨綠、霧淺灰及霧櫻粉 4 隻顏色選擇，顏色均走清新鮮艷搶眼路線，應該會頗受年青人歡迎。而在設計上，Galaxy A36 及 A56 其實差不多，兩者均內建了 6.7 吋 Super AMOLED 熒幕及三主鏡設計，最能將兩機分辨出來的只有機邊：A36 採用淨色設計，而 A56 就加入了拉絲紋理。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1297666" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250314_135638-694x523.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="523" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250314_135638-694x523.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250314_135638.jpg 1195w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1297668" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250314_135645-694x523.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="523" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250314_135645-694x523.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250314_135645.jpg 1195w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲今次 Samsung 推出的全新 Galaxy A 系中階機：Galaxy A36（第一張）及 Galaxy A56（第二張），均採用了鮮艷搶眼的配色，針對年青用家族羣。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1297669" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250314_140758-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250314_140758-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250314_140758.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1297670" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250314_141105-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250314_141105-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250314_141105.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲無論是 Galaxy A36（第一張）還是 Galaxy A56（第二張），機背依然採用了強化玻璃物料製造。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1297672" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250314_140808-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250314_140808-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250314_140808.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1297673" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250314_141055-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250314_141055-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250314_141055.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Galaxy A36（第一張）及 A56（第二張），同樣在機身右側設有開關鍵及音量鍵，亦同樣採用了二段式設計。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1297674" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250314_140814-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250314_140814-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250314_140814.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1297675" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250314_141050-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250314_141050-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250314_141050.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Galaxy A36 及 A56 其實在機身設計上十分相似，最易分辨兩者的地方，就是機側：A36 採用純銀色設計（第一張）而 A56 就加入了拉絲紋理（第二張）。</p><h2>兩機同採三主鏡設計配置有異成像合理</h2><p>至於相機方面，Samsung Galaxy A36 及 A56 均內建了 3 個主鏡頭設計，而且今代並非再採用三個獨立鏡頭組，而是使用了一個黑玻璃片保護三個鏡頭，令設計上終於與上代有少許分別。至於鏡頭配置方面，兩機同樣採用了主攝鏡 + 超廣角鏡 + 微距鏡的配置，不過像素上就有分別：Galaxy A36 的主攝鏡、超廣角鏡及微距鏡像素分別為 5,000 萬、800 萬及 500 萬，而 Galaxy A56 的主攝鏡、超廣角鏡及微距鏡像素則分別為 5,000 萬、1,200 萬及 500 萬。而兩機前鏡均同樣採開孔式設計，像素亦同樣為 1,200 萬。至於成像方面，老實説作為中階機，筆者對它們的期望不算很大，不過出來的效果依然算不俗，雖然以人像模式拍攝虛化效果會有少許「假」，但整體來説仍算不錯，唯一是它們畢竟未有內建長焦鏡，所以拍攝遠物時不但不能拍得很遠，清晰度亦不太理想。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1297676" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250314_140852-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250314_140852-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250314_140852.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1297677" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250314_141112-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250314_141112-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250314_141112.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲鏡頭方面，A36（第一張）及 A56（第二張）均採用了 3 主鏡設計，兩機同樣內建了 5,000 萬像素主攝鏡及 500 萬像素微距鏡，唯一是超廣角鏡，A36 只支援至 800 萬像素，而 A56 就支援至 1,200 萬。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1297679" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143541-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143541-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143541-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1297680" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143545-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143545-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143545-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1297681" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143548-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143548-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143548-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1297682" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143553-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143553-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143553-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲先來看 Galaxy A36 鏡頭表示，筆者在日間室外分別以超廣角鏡（第一張）、主攝鏡 1x（第二張）、主攝鏡 2x（第三張）及主攝鏡 4x（第四張）拍攝，大家可以見到成像不算十分有驚喜，但總算清晰度高，顏色還原度亦不錯。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1297684" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143457-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143457-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143457-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1297685" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143459-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143459-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143459-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1297686" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143501-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143501-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143501-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1297687" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143504-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143504-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143504-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲至於 Galaxy A56 的成像方面，筆者以相同焦距試拍，結果覺得它們與 A36 的成像效果差不多，不過觀感上以 Galaxy A56 拍攝似乎清晰度更高一點，相片的立體感亦較佳。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1297683" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143556-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143556-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143556-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1297688" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143507-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143507-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143507-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲不過始終兩機均未設長焦鏡配置，所以使用主攝鏡配合數碼變焦拍攝遠物，無論是 Galaxy A36（第一張）還是 A56（第二張）其實也只屬一般。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1297689" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143419-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143419-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143419-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1297690" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143443-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143443-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143443-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲至於微距鏡方面，無論是使用 Galaxy A36（第一張）還是 A56（第二張）拍攝，效果也算不錯，當中 A56 的成像似乎更好一點。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1297691" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143816-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143816-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143816-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1297692" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143804-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143804-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143804-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲至於在室內拍攝物件，筆者也覺得 Galaxy A56（第二張）出來的效果會比 A36（第一張）好，但差距不算遠。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1297694 alignnone" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143353-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143353-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143353-scaled.jpg 675w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1297695 alignnone" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143324-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143324-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143324-scaled.jpg 675w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲至於人像拍攝方面，筆者也覺得 Galaxy A56（右）出來的效果比較理想，A36（左）拍出來感覺會較青，色準不算好。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1297696 alignnone" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143633-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143633-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143633-scaled.jpg 675w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1297697 alignnone" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143707-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143707-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143707-scaled.jpg 675w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲至於前鏡效果方面，同樣是 Galaxy A56（右）出來的效果會比 A36（左）來得自然及理想。</p><br /><b>
